      "content": "that makes sense. i've been looking at the FOIA stuff but it's so much to sift through and it's all so dry. i feel like if i could just find a way to cross-reference the telemetry data with the gaps in the visual footage, i'd see the truth. what kind of specific technical discrepancies or \"anomalies\" in the lunar landing data should i be looking for to find signs of this cover-up?",
